course_title: PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT AND ENGAGEMENT 1: DEVELOPING YOUR PROFESSIONAL IDENTITY
description: Explore aspects of professional identity and how to become more engaged with the pharmacy profession. Explore personal values, skills, and strengths and identify their implications for patient care and professional practice. Engage in continuing professional and interprofessional development to promote quality patient care and advocacy.
